</ul><p>※ 本文與 行政院農業委員會 林務局  <a href="http://www.forest.gov.tw/" style="color: rgb(71, 106, 38); text-decoration: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22.5px; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 233);" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="https://c1.staticflickr.com/7/6239/6307752589_341e4d1ef0_t.jpg" style="border: 0px; color: rgb(71, 106, 38); text-decoration: underline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 22.5px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; width: 100px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 233);" /></a>合作刊登</p>
<p> </p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-14 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/118">生態旅遊</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/224">物種保育</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-11 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/42874">濕地故事</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-25 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/2493">獵人</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/25104">台灣白魚</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/45557">綠保標章</a></div></div></div><div id="block-views-author-block" class="block">
      <h2 class="block-title">作者</h2>
    <div class="field-items">
     
              
    <div class="content clearfix">
    <a href="/node/200155" title="廖靜蕙" class="author-link">廖靜蕙</a>
      <div class="field field-name-field-photo field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/node/200155"><img src="http://e-info.org.tw/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/cliao.jpg?itok=xfBJJ9_-" width="220" height="220" alt="" /></a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>環境記者／自由撰稿人。從事社工10餘年，認知到畢竟是人的社會，再弱勢的人都可以為自己發言，決定轉投生態保育，為無法以人類語言發聲的生命與土地寫報導。現居臺北市，與貓先生、龜小姐，微曦中閱讀，斗室中寫作。個人粉專「<a href="https://www.facebook.com/MathinksDelivery/">小麻通訊</a>」。</p>
</div></div></div>    </div>

           
  </div>
