</ul></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-14 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/246">自然資源管理</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/228">森林</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-11 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/42874">濕地故事</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-25 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4199">嘉明湖</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/42719">廖靜蕙</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/524">生態旅遊</a></div></div></div><div id="block-views-author-block" class="block">
